comments:
I noticed that color would only matter with the round shape, so I basically memorized the bufi- zeti- etc, and tried to remember the e/h based on the color of the round shape.
The second part was obtusely unintuitive, though. I'm guessing that the hope was that participants would learn to associate what words would mean for the partner and try to choose accordingly, or maybe come up with variants to define the color, but it was just confusing and felt random.
